# Django QR Code Generator

A web application built with Django that generates QR codes from text or URLs.

## Features

- Generate QR codes instantly
- Supports text and website URLs
- Download generated QR codes
- Clean and responsive interface

## Tech Stack

- Python
- Django
- HTML
- CSS
- qrcode Library
- Pillow

## Project Structure

- Django Views
- Templates
- Forms
- Dynamic Files

## Future Improvements

- QR Code History
- User Authentication
- Colored QR Codes
- Custom Logo QR Codes


